    "excerpt": "Best places to experience autumn colors in Pakistan",
    "content": "A \nreel\n featuring autumn colours of Northeren Pakistan\n\n1: Ghizar & Phandar Valley\n\nNot known by most tourists, Ghizar valley is perfect for those who value remote peaceful areas over Touristy Destinations. During Autumn season the color of river turns green, blue and all the trees turn yellow. You would want to stop at every garden, which makes the travel more beautiful than the destinations.\n\n2: Baltistan\n\nFrom cold desert contrasting with Autumn colours to huge gardens of Ghwari, Baltistan has a lot of unique destinations that will make you wish you had time to experience more.\n\nAutumn at Upper Kachura lake\n\nAutumn colors of Katpana Desert\n\nJoin our curated \nGroup\n tours or get a glimpse of\n these majestic landscape!",
